        <video  src={autofill} class="w-5/6 h-3/5 object-contain mx-auto" 
          autoplay  muted loop playsinline  style="pointer-events: none;"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">‚ö° Smart Autocomplete</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Leverage Google's autocomplete for efficient searching.</p>
